div.p: Loading basic identity information from a Substrate based chain, implementing the Identity pallet, is fast enough and does not need an caching.
To retrieve detailed information about an accounts actions, an indexing is necessary. All information fetched during the indexing is parsed and stored in the SQL database for faster access.
